Finite state machine
initial state
list of states
conditions for each state

stand
    initial
    velocity 0
walk
    velocity between 0 and 5
run
    velocity > 5

Create AnimationController
add animation states (Animation and condition)
set initial state
call play sub with params

e.g.

# Basic initialisation
AnimationController ac = Oyster::AnimationController::new();
ac->addState(standing, sub {a == 0})
ac->addState(walking, sub { a > 0 && a < 5})
ac->addState(running, sub {a > 5})
ac->play(velocity)

# Then do
ac->getCurrentAnimation()
